</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#DEB887><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub73.ezboard.com/ucaulfield.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Caulfield</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>poon</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/22/01 12:49:50 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How much am I missing?</span><hr size=1> Maybe they should make a server which works with the game's already existing PvP methods then. Like, make it so if someone challenges you to a duel and you are within 5 levels but decline, then you automatically lose all the money you have on you to them (same if you zone while engaged in a duel). And then also set it so you can't join or start a guild unless you turn in the child of order thing and enable PvP. It would be interesting.<br>
<br>
,Caul <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=FAEBD7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub73.ezboard.com/uvachir.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vachir</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Tavern Regular</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/22/01 1:31:54 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How much am I missing?</span><hr size=1> For example of why red &gt; blue server see thread here:<br>
