ng are excellent at keeping a caster in mid cast from hitting you with a spell. With no other alternative you can use invisability or hide to remove yourself from an opponents target box, this will not stop a cast in progress but so long as you don't get targeted again you won't get hit with any more spells.  This is a good example of how PvP is more complex than PvE.<br>
